   <p>In handling of the foresaid points for orders sake, is considered,
<list>
         <item>1. The <hi>meaning,</hi> or such <hi>points of do<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ctrine</hi> as are necessarie to bee knowne thereof.</item>
         <item>2. The <hi>duties</hi> to be learned thereby.</item>
         <item>3. The <hi>comforts</hi> that Gods pleople may gather thence.</item>
      </list>
   </p>
